sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODHC as ODH Controller
    participant KFC as KF Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as Culling Reconciler

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation (Auth Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>MutWH: /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>TLS (service cert)
    Note right of MutWH: Sets reconciliation lock<br/>Resolves ImageStream→digest<br/>Injects CA bundles<br/>Injects MLflow env vars<br/>Injects proxy settings
    MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook CR
    K8sAPI->>ValWH: /validate-notebook-v1<br/>TLS (service cert)
    Note right of ValWH: Validates MLflow annotation<br/>safety on running notebooks
    ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Admitted

    ODHC->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR<br/>SA token
    Note right of ODHC: Creates in user namespace:<br/>ServiceAccount, kube-rbac-proxy Service,<br/>ConfigMap, NetworkPolicy, Secret
    ODHC->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>(controller namespace)<br/>parentRef→data-science-gateway<br/>backendRef→kube-rbac-proxy:8443
    ODHC->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>(user namespace)<br/>Allows cross-namespace routing
    ODHC->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>system:auth-delegator
    ODHC->>K8sAPI: Remove reconciliation lock

    KFC->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR<br/>SA token
    Note right of KFC: Creates StatefulSet<br/>(with kube-rbac-proxy sidecar)<br/>Creates Service (80→8888)

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: User Accesses Notebook (Auth Mode)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}/*<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS TLS (service cert)
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token valid
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>verb=get, resource=notebooks<br/>name={notebook}, ns={ns}
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Access granted
    KRBP->>Notebook: Forward to localhost<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
    Notebook-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Response

    Note over Culler,Notebook: Flow 3: Idle Notebook Culling

    Culler->>Notebook: GET /api/kernels, /api/terminals<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP (in-cluster)
    Notebook-->>Culler: Activity status
    Note right of Culler: If idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME
    Culler->>K8sAPI: Patch Notebook status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>SA token
    KFC->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>SA token
